This paper deals with the problem of secure communication over a wiretap channel, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of polar coding is a common technique in communication engineering (cs.CE) and signal processing (cs.SI). The paper also mentions the use of randomness as a limited resource, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
